remarks_new_class.description: A text field in the Remarks section to specify the new nonimmigrant class.

form_footer_barcode.description: A PDF417 barcode field located at the bottom of the page used for USCIS data capture.

page_footer_barcode.description: A PDF417 barcode located at the bottom of the page, used for system processing and data capture of the form information.

preparer_given_name.description: The given name (first name) of the person who prepared the application on behalf of the applicant.

preparer_family_name.description: The family name (last name) of the person who prepared the application on behalf of the applicant.

footer_pdf417_barcode.description: A PDF417 barcode field located at the bottom of the page, used for automated data capture by USCIS.

interpreter_given_name.description: The given name (first name) of the interpreter who assisted with the application.

part_1_passport_number.description: The passport number used for the most recent entry into the United States, if applicable.

physical_address_state.description: The state of the applicant's current physical address, selected from a standard list of US states.

preparer_business_name.description: The name of the business or organization that the preparer is affiliated with, if applicable.

interpreter_family_name.description: The family name (last name) of the interpreter who assisted with the application.

interpreter_mobile_phone.description: The mobile telephone number for the interpreter, if they have one.

remarks_granted_checkbox.description: A checkbox in the Remarks section indicating that the application has been granted.

uscis_use_only_fee_stamp.description: A large area designated for the USCIS fee stamp, located in the top center of the form.

interpreter_business_name.description: The name of the business or organization the interpreter is affiliated with, if applicable.

interpreter_daytime_phone.description: The daytime telephone number where the interpreter can be reached.

physical_address_zip_code.description: The 5-digit ZIP code for the applicant's current physical address.

attorney_info_g28_attached.description: Checkbox to indicate if Form G-28, Notice of Entry of Appearance as Attorney or Accredited Representative, is attached.

page_footer_barcode_page_5.description: A PDF417 barcode used for document processing, located at the bottom of the page.

page_footer_barcode_page_6.description: A PDF417 barcode used for automated data capture and processing of the form information.

part_1_country_of_issuance.description: The country that issued the passport or travel document used for the most recent entry.

part_1_date_status_expires.description: Enter the expiration date of your current nonimmigrant status in mm/dd/yyyy format.

processing_info_date_filed.description: The date the application was filed, formatted as mm/dd/yyyy.

uscis_use_only_sd_to_value.description: The text value associated with the 'S/D to' field in the USCIS Use Only section, likely indicating a specific status or date.

mailing_address_unit_number.description: The specific number for the apartment, suite, or floor indicated by the checkbox. Located in Part 1, Item 4.

physical_address_abroad_flr.description: A checkbox indicating that the physical address abroad includes a floor number.

physical_address_abroad_ste.description: A checkbox indicating that the physical address abroad includes a suite number.

uscis_use_only_action_block.description: A large area designated for the USCIS action block, located in the top right of the form.

uscis_use_only_dates_to_day.description: The day component of the 'To' date in the 'Dates' subsection of the 'For USCIS Use Only' area.

application_type_school_name.description: The name of the school the applicant will attend, if applicable, as an Academic Student, Vocational Student, or Exchange Visitor.

footer_pdf417_barcode_page_4.description: A PDF417 2D barcode located at the bottom of the page, used for automated data processing and capture of the information entered on the form.

part_1_mailing_address_floor.description: A checkbox to indicate that the mailing address unit is a floor (Flr.). Part of Item 4 in Information About You.

part_1_mailing_address_state.description: The state for the applicant's U.S. mailing address, selected from a dropdown list. Part of Item 4 in Information About You.

physical_address_unit_number.description: A text field for entering the specific apartment, suite, or floor number for the applicant's current physical address.

preparer_mobile_phone_number.description: The mobile telephone number of the preparer, if they have one.

uscis_use_only_date_from_day.description: The day component for the 'From' date in the USCIS Use Only section.

uscis_use_only_dates_to_year.description: The year component of the 'To' date in the 'Dates' subsection of the 'For USCIS Use Only' area.

uscis_use_only_returned_date.description: A field within the 'For USCIS Use Only' section used to record the date the application was returned.

additional_information_3_text.description: A large text area for providing additional information or explanations related to a specific page, part, and item number in section 3 of Part 8.

additional_information_4_text.description: A large text area for providing additional information related to a specific page, part, and item number in section 4 of Part 8.

additional_information_5_text.description: A large text area for providing additional information related to item number 5 in Part 8.

additional_information_6_text.description: A large text area for providing additional information related to item number 6 in Part 8.

mailing_address_unit_type_apt.description: Checkbox indicating that the mailing address unit type is an Apartment (Apt.). Located in Part 1, Item 4.

mailing_address_unit_type_ste.description: Checkbox indicating that the mailing address unit type is a Suite (Ste.). Located in Part 1, Item 4.

part_1_travel_document_number.description: The travel document number used for the most recent entry into the United States, if applicable.

physical_address_city_or_town.description: The city or town of the applicant's current physical address.

preparer_daytime_phone_number.description: The daytime telephone number where the preparer can be reached.

processing_information_header.description: Header field for Part 3: Processing Information.

uscis_use_only_date_from_year.description: The year component for the 'From' date in the USCIS Use Only section.

uscis_use_only_dates_to_month.description: The month component of the 'To' date in the 'Dates' subsection of the 'For USCIS Use Only' area.

uscis_use_only_sd_to_checkbox.description: A checkbox for the 'S/D to' field in the USCIS Use Only section.

additional_information_barcode.description: A PDF417 barcode located at the bottom of the Additional Information page, used for automated data capture and processing of the form's contents.

attorney_info_state_bar_number.description: The state bar number of the attorney representing the applicant, if applicable.

physical_address_unit_type_apt.description: A checkbox to indicate that the physical address unit type is an apartment (Apt.).

physical_address_unit_type_ste.description: A checkbox to indicate that the physical address unit type is a suite (Ste.).

processing_info_form_type_i129.description: Checkbox selecting Form I-129, Petition for a Nonimmigrant Worker, as the form type if 'Yes' was answered to Item Number 2 or 3.

processing_info_form_type_i539.description: Checkbox selecting Form I-539, Application to Extend/Change Nonimmigrant Status, as the form type if 'Yes' was answered to Item Number 2 or 3.

uscis_use_only_date_from_month.description: The month component for the 'From' date in the USCIS Use Only section.

additional_information_a_number.description: The Alien Registration Number (A-Number) of the individual, if any. This field is typically prepopulated from page 1.

application_type_only_applicant.description: A checkbox indicating that the individual is the only applicant in Part 2, Question 3.

mailing_address_in_care_of_name.description: The name of the person who receives mail at this address, if different from the applicant. Located in Part 1, Item 4.

part_1_mailing_address_zip_code.description: The 5-digit ZIP code for the applicant's U.S. mailing address. Part of Item 4 in Information About You.

physical_address_floor_checkbox.description: A checkbox indicating that the following number refers to a floor level for the applicant's current physical address.

uscis_use_only_resubmitted_date.description: A field within the 'For USCIS Use Only' section used to record the date the application was resubmitted.

additional_info_military_unit_no.description: Checkbox indicating 'No' for question 8.a: Have you EVER served in, been a member of, assisted, or participated in any military unit, paramilitary unit, police unit, self-defense unit, vigilante unit, rebel group, guerrilla group, militia, insurgent organization, or any other armed group?

application_type_sevis_id_number.description: The applicant's Student and Exchange Visitor Information System (SEVIS) ID Number, if applicable.

information_about_you_given_name.description: The applicant's given name or first name as part of their full legal name.

physical_address_abroad_province.description: The province of the applicant's physical address located outside of the United States.

preparer_certification_signature.description: The ink signature of the preparer. This field cannot be signed electronically and must be signed after printing.

additional_info_killing_person_no.description: A checkbox indicating 'No' for question 7.b. asking if the applicant has ever participated in killing any person.

additional_info_military_unit_yes.description: Checkbox indicating 'Yes' for question 8.a: Have you EVER served in, been a member of, assisted, or participated in any military unit, paramilitary unit, police unit, self-defense unit, vigilante unit, rebel group, guerrilla group, militia, insurgent organization, or any other armed group?

additional_info_sexual_contact_no.description: A checkbox indicating 'No' for question 7.d. asking if the applicant has ever engaged in non-consensual sexual contact or relations.

additional_information_given_name.description: The given name (first name) of the individual providing additional information in Part 8. This field is typically prepopulated from page 1.

applicant_certification_signature.description: The handwritten ink signature of the applicant certifying the information provided. This field cannot be signed electronically.

application_type_change_of_status.description: A checkbox indicating that the applicant is applying for a change of status under Part 2, Question 1.

information_about_you_family_name.description: The applicant's family name or last name as part of their full legal name.

information_about_you_middle_name.description: The applicant's middle name, if applicable, as part of their full legal name.

part_2_application_type_extension.description: Check this box if you are applying for an extension of stay in your current status. This is one of the mutually exclusive options in Part 2, Question 1.

additional_info_ever_filed_i485_no.description: A checkbox indicating 'No' to the question: Have you EVER filed Form I-485, Application to Register Permanent Residence or Adjust Status?

additional_info_injuring_person_no.description: A checkbox indicating 'No' for question 7.c. asking if the applicant has ever intentionally and severely injured any person.

additional_info_killing_person_yes.description: Indicates 'Yes' to whether the applicant has EVER ordered, incited, called for, committed, assisted, helped with, or otherwise participated in killing any person. If 'Yes', an explanation must be provided in Part 8.

additional_info_sexual_contact_yes.description: A checkbox indicating 'Yes' for question 7.d. asking if the applicant has ever engaged in non-consensual sexual contact or relations. If selected, an explanation must be provided in Part 8.

additional_information_family_name.description: The family name (last name) of the individual providing additional information in Part 8. This field is typically prepopulated from page 1.

additional_information_middle_name.description: The middle name (if applicable) of the individual providing additional information in Part 8. This field is typically prepopulated from page 1.

additional_information_page_number.description: The page number of the form to which the additional information in this section refers.

applicant_info_group_weapon_use_no.description: Checkbox for 'No' response to question 9: Have you EVER been a member of, assisted, or participated in any group, unit, or organization of any kind in which you or other persons used or threatened to use any type of weapon against any person or threatened to do so?

applicant_info_weapon_transport_no.description: Checkbox for 'No' response to question 10: Have you EVER sold, provided, or transported weapons, or assisted any person in selling, providing, or transporting weapons, which, you knew or believed would be used against another person?

interpreter_certification_language.description: The language in which the interpreter is fluent and has interpreted the application, as stated in the certification section of Part 6.

application_type_total_people_count.description: The total number of people, including the primary applicant, included in this application. A Form I-539A is required for each co-applicant.

attorney_info_g28_attached_checkbox.description: A checkbox to be selected by an attorney or accredited representative if Form G-28 is attached.

information_about_you_date_of_birth.description: The applicant's date of birth, formatted as mm/dd/yyyy.

interpreter_certification_signature.description: The ink signature of the interpreter. This field must be signed by hand and cannot be signed electronically.

part_1_information_about_you_header.description: Text field or header area for Part 1: Information About You.

part_1_mailing_address_city_or_town.description: The city or town for the applicant's U.S. mailing address. Part of Item 4 in Information About You.

physical_address_abroad_postal_code.description: The postal code of the applicant's physical address located outside of the United States.

preparer_contact_info_email_address.description: The email address of the person who prepared the application, if applicable.

principal_applicant_passport_number.description: The current passport number of the principal applicant if it differs from the information provided in Part 1.

additional_info_ever_employed_us_yes.description: Indicates that the applicant has been employed in the United States since their last admission or status change (Question 14). If selected, details must be provided in Part 8.

additional_info_religious_beliefs_no.description: Checkbox indicating 'No' for question 7.e: Have you EVER ordered, incited, called for, committed, assisted, helped with, or otherwise participated in limiting or denying any person's ability to exercise religious beliefs?

additional_info_torture_genocide_yes.description: Indicates 'Yes' to whether the applicant has EVER ordered, incited, called for, committed, assisted, helped with, or otherwise participated in acts involving torture or genocide. If 'Yes', an explanation must be provided in Part 8.

additional_information_3_item_number.description: The item number associated with the additional information provided in section 3 of Part 8.

additional_information_3_part_number.description: The part number associated with the additional information provided in section 3 of Part 8.

additional_information_4_item_number.description: The item number associated with the additional information provided in section 4 of Part 8.

additional_information_4_page_number.description: The page number associated with the additional information provided in section 4 of Part 8.

additional_information_4_part_number.description: The part number associated with the additional information provided in section 4 of Part 8.

additional_information_5_item_number.description: The item number associated with the additional information provided in section 5 of Part 8.

additional_information_5_page_number.description: The page number associated with the additional information provided in section 5 of Part 8.

additional_information_5_part_number.description: The part number associated with the additional information provided in section 5 of Part 8.

additional_information_6_item_number.description: The item number to which the additional information in item 6 refers.

additional_information_6_page_number.description: The page number to which the additional information in item 6 refers.

additional_information_6_part_number.description: The part number to which the additional information in item 6 refers.

applicant_contact_info_email_address.description: The applicant's email address, if they have one.

physical_address_abroad_city_or_town.description: The city or town of the applicant's physical address located outside of the United States.

processing_info_separate_petition_no.description: Checkbox indicating that the application is not based on a separate petition or application for a spouse, child, or parent.

processing_info_uscis_receipt_number.description: The USCIS Receipt Number associated with the petition or application, required if 'Yes' was answered to Item Number 2 or 3 in Part 3.

additional_info_arrested_convicted_no.description: Indicates 'No' to whether the applicant has been arrested or convicted of any criminal offense since last entering the United States.

additional_info_j_exchange_visitor_no.description: Indicates that the applicant is not and has never been a J-1 exchange visitor or J-2 dependent (Question 15).

additional_info_religious_beliefs_yes.description: Checkbox indicating 'Yes' for question 7.e: Have you EVER ordered, incited, called for, committed, assisted, helped with, or otherwise participated in limiting or denying any person's ability to exercise religious beliefs?

part_2_application_type_reinstatement.description: Check this box if you are applying for reinstatement to student status. This is one of the mutually exclusive options in Part 2, Question 1.

processing_info_beneficiary_last_name.description: The last name of the beneficiary or applicant if the petition or application is pending with USCIS.

additional_info_arrested_convicted_yes.description: Indicates 'Yes' to whether the applicant has been arrested or convicted of any criminal offense since last entering the United States. If 'Yes', an explanation must be provided in Part 8.

additional_info_detention_facility_yes.description: Checkbox indicating 'Yes' for question 8.b: Have you EVER worked, volunteered, or otherwise served in any prison, jail, prison camp, detention facility, labor camp, or any other situation that involved detaining persons?

additional_info_j_exchange_visitor_yes.description: Indicates that the applicant is or has been a J-1 exchange visitor or J-2 dependent (Question 15). If selected, status maintenance dates must be provided in Part 8.

additional_info_removal_proceedings_no.description: Indicates that the applicant is not currently in removal proceedings (Question 13).

information_about_you_country_of_birth.description: The name of the country where the applicant was born.

interpreter_contact_info_email_address.description: The email address of the interpreter, as requested in Part 6, item 5.

mailing_address_street_number_and_name.description: The street number and name for the applicant's U.S. mailing address or safe address. Located in Part 1, Item 4.

processing_info_beneficiary_first_name.description: The first name of the beneficiary or applicant if the petition or application is pending with USCIS.

uscis_use_only_relocated_received_date.description: A field within the 'For USCIS Use Only' section used to record the date the relocated application was received.

action_block_applicant_interviewed_date.description: The date on which the applicant was interviewed, located within the Action Block section.

physical_address_street_number_and_name.description: A text field for entering the street number and name of the applicant's current physical address.

preparer_certification_date_of_signature.description: The date the preparer signed the form, formatted as mm/dd/yyyy.

applicant_certification_date_of_signatur.description: The date the applicant signed the form, formatted as mm/dd/yyyy.

attorney_info_uscis_online_account_numbe.description: The 12-digit USCIS Online Account Number for the attorney or accredited representative. Do not include dashes.

uscis_use_only_place_under_docket_contro.description: A checkbox indicating whether to place the application under docket control, located in the 'For USCIS Use Only' section.

additional_info_in_removal_proceedings_y.description: Indicates 'Yes' to whether the applicant is currently in removal proceedings. If yes, an explanation must be provided in Part 8.

applicant_contact_info_mobile_phone_numb.description: The applicant's mobile telephone number, if they have one.

information_about_you_date_of_last_arriv.description: The date of the applicant's most recent entry into the United States, formatted as mm/dd/yyyy.

part_1_i94_arrival_departure_record_numb.description: The Form I-94 Arrival-Departure Record Number provided during the most recent entry into the United States.

processing_info_status_extended_until_da.description: The date until which the applicant requests their current or requested status be extended. Format: mm/dd/yyyy.

additional_info_immigrant_petition_filed.description: Checkbox indicating 'No' to the question: 'Has an immigrant petition EVER been filed for you?' in Part 4, Item 4.

additional_info_immigrant_visa_applicant.description: Checkbox indicating 'No' to the question: 'Are you an applicant for an immigrant visa?' in Part 4, Item 3.

applicant_contact_info_daytime_phone_num.description: The applicant's daytime telephone number where they can be reached during business hours.

interpreter_certification_date_of_signat.description: The date the interpreter signed the form, formatted as mm/dd/yyyy.

part_1_mailing_address_same_as_physical_.description: A checkbox to indicate 'Yes' if the mailing address is the same as the physical address. If checked, skip to Item Number 7. Part of Item 5 in Information About You.

additional_info_immigrant_petition_filed.description: Checkbox indicating 'Yes' to the question: 'Has an immigrant petition EVER been filed for you?' in Part 4, Item 4.

additional_info_immigrant_visa_applicant.description: Checkbox indicating 'Yes' to the question: 'Are you an applicant for an immigrant visa?' in Part 4, Item 3.

additional_info_received_weapons_trainin.description: Indicates 'No' to whether the applicant has ever received any weapons training, paramilitary training, or other military-type training.

information_about_you_country_of_citizen.description: The country of citizenship or nationality for the applicant.

information_about_you_social_security_nu.description: The applicant's 9-digit U.S. Social Security Number, if applicable. Enter numbers only without dashes.

principal_applicant_passport_expiration_.description: The expiration date of the principal applicant's current passport in mm/dd/yyyy format.

processing_info_extension_based_on_famil.description: A checkbox for Part 3, Question 2, indicating 'No' if the application is not based on an extension or change of status already granted to a spouse, child, or parent.

remarks_still_within_period_of_stay_chec.description: A checkbox in the Remarks section indicating the applicant is still within their period of stay.

additional_info_received_weapons_trainin.description: Indicates 'Yes' to whether the applicant has ever received any weapons training, paramilitary training, or other military-type training. If yes, an explanation must be provided in Part 8.

application_type_status_change_effective.description: A text field for the requested effective date of the status change, formatted as mm/dd/yyyy, in Part 2, Question 2.

information_about_you_mailing_address_sa.description: A checkbox indicating 'No' to the question of whether the mailing address is the same as the physical address. If checked, physical address details must be provided in Item Number 6.

processing_info_extension_based_on_famil.description: A checkbox for Part 3, Question 2, indicating 'Yes' if the application is based on an extension or change of status already granted to a spouse, child, or parent.

additional_info_physical_address_abroad_.description: The country of the applicant's physical address abroad, as part of the additional information about the principal applicant in Part 4, Item 2.

additional_info_violated_nonimmigrant_st.description: Indicates 'No' to whether the applicant has ever violated the terms of their current nonimmigrant status.

information_about_you_alien_registration.description: The applicant's 9-digit Alien Registration Number (A-Number), if any. Do not include dashes.

part_1_passport_travel_document_expirati.description: The expiration date of the passport or travel document used for the most recent entry, formatted as mm/dd/yyyy.

principal_applicant_foreign_address_unit.description: The specific apartment, suite, or floor number for the principal applicant's physical address abroad.

additional_info_violated_nonimmigrant_st.description: Indicates 'Yes' to whether the applicant has ever violated the terms of their current nonimmigrant status. If yes, an explanation must be provided in Part 8.

principal_applicant_passport_country_of_.description: The country that issued the principal applicant's current passport, as requested in Part 4, Item 1.

uscis_use_only_applicant_interviewed_on_.description: A checkbox for USCIS use only to indicate if the applicant was interviewed.

information_about_you_uscis_online_accou.description: The applicant's 12-digit USCIS Online Account Number, if any. Do not include dashes.

principal_applicant_foreign_address_unit.description: A checkbox indicating that the unit type for the physical address abroad is an apartment (Apt.).

processing_info_separate_petition_yes_pe.description: Checkbox indicating that the application is based on a separate petition or application previously filed and currently pending with USCIS.

processing_info_separate_petition_yes_fi.description: Checkbox indicating that the application is based on a separate petition or application filed with this Form I-539 for a spouse, child, or parent.

principal_applicant_foreign_address_stre.description: The street number and name for the principal applicant's physical address abroad.
